{"tid":713660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"忘形情侶漫步東區走廊   司機鬧爆：唔好累人","createTime":"2018-06-23T04:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T12:40:40.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0c5eabb4e40ac0de706aa0ce12061f6a8d421b52","tid":713660,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:26:46.000Z","msg":"拍拖來來去去都係行街、睇戲、食飯，冇啲新意！有兩名年輕人就想出「新橋」，捨易取難在東區走廊散步，甜蜜得羨煞旁人，莫非真是愈難愈愛？<br />\n<br />\n有讀者向東網爆料，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>拍得一對年約廿歲的年輕情侶不惜以命相搏，於東區走廊公路上漫步</strong></span>。不過司機似乎對情侶的行為大感不滿，直指「喂你兩個無錢搭車呀？」，又以粗口怒斥兩人，「你戇鳩㗎？你兩個究竟係咪黐線㗎，你唔好累死人呀！」。男生連聲回應「唔係」，看見司機拍片時更以手擋鏡保護女友，非常體貼！不過，行唔行，下次最好都係行番商場吧啦，危險呀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jTWeCBl5X3pH4mdQe269JQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/4500952ac73b867359cf231b4fb7362c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FjTWeCBl5X3pH4mdQe269JQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F4500952ac73b867359cf231b4fb7362c&h=dc3cd50e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44e7fca98385b4228f77d872c2c6879db61e2608","tid":713660,"uid":76115,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:27:49.000Z","msg":"真係以死相搏<br />\n勇過學獨聯班低能仔"},{"pid":"3872bb30ef2fb63781ef3bc16c3f111956a1b532","tid":713660,"uid":149902,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:28:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b96e01dddad93d4d3cbd41c5bf2f3ddfc4228de4","tid":713660,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T05:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452e7e23485abbe647783184a55b1672b9367564","tid":713660,"uid":15815,"like":1,"di